  "name": "warehouse-query",
  "body": "<p>Hi {{ticket.requester.first_name}},&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif;\">Thank you for your message.&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif;\">We have reached out to the warehouse to query the state of your return.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif;\">Once there is more information, we will update you.&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif;\">We hope you enjoy the rest of your day.&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif;\">Kind regards,&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif;\">Mac Group Customer Service&nbsp;</span></p>",
